description:
These cookies are a cake-like version of chocolate chips and are very full of chips and nuts. they are excellent. this isn't originally my recipe, i adopted it.
if you need conversions, here they are: ( thank you treble :) )
for anyone who needs conversions, here they are: 1 1/4 cup butter, 2/3 cup each brown and white sugars, 1 1/2 tsp.vanilla, 4 cups flour, 1 1/2 tsp. soda, 3/4 tsp. salt, 2 (12 oz) packages chocolate chips, and just under 1 cup walnuts.
